core.model.management

Class AbstractStatefulModelManager<E,S>

  • java.lang.Object
    • core.model.management.AbstractModelManager<E>
      • core.model.management.AbstractStatefulModelManager<E,S>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - the type of the model to manage.
    S - the type of the model state's description.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    IModelManager<E>, IStatefulModelManager<E,S>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    EcoreModelManager

    public abstract class AbstractStatefulModelManager<E,S>
extends AbstractModelManager<E>
implements IStatefulModelManager<E,S>
    an AbstractStatefulModelManager generic abstract class that is used to factor the common interface and state of all stateful concrete model manager classes.

    This class also provides wrapper methods for the basic model import/export operations, allowing to handle state management accordingly upon executing any of them. By default the states of a model are stored and handled by a LinkedList.

    It must be specialized by all concrete model manager classes.
    Author:
    Bachar Rima
    See Also:
    AbstractModelState

      • AbstractStatefulModelManager

        public AbstractStatefulModelManager(java.lang.String path)
        Creates a model manager to manage the model associated to a specific path and initializes the collection of model states as a LinkedList. The importation details of the model associated to the path will be explicited in the constructors of the concrete implementations of this class.

        path - the path associated to the model to be managed by this model manager

                                    java.util.Collection<AbstractModelState<E,S>> states)
        Creates a model manager to manage the model associated to a specific path and initializes the collection of model states associated with this model manager's managed model using the provided collection of model states. The importation details of the model associated to the path will be explicited in the constructors of the concrete implementations of this class.

        path - the path associated to the model to be managed by this model manager
        states - the value initializing the states collection associated with this model manager's managed model
